Split out uploading and social publishing to ReviewPublisher. Reviews automatically uploaded and shared when added to ReviewQueue via ReviewPublisher using BackendConsumer and SocialConsumer.
PresentUsersFeed now just listens for stuff.
Organised MyGeneralLibrary into packages
Added deleting from backend back in via BackendReviewDeleter
Moved setting of user and thus AuthorsStamp to ApplicationInstance. Removed getAuthorsFeed from PresenterContext and replaced with get getFactoryReviewsFeed
Added multi-path update for Firebase when uploading review
Reversed some changes to moving of RelationalDb package to General library.
Reorganised packaages to better reflect the modular nature of the various application contexts

Quick fix of bug that stopped reviews with special characters in the title uploading to firebase because of illegal token in path. This was due to Tags including the special token. Removed special tokens in adjustTagsIfNeccessary code but need more robust and universal solution.
Added getDeletesMap to FirebaseStructure for proper structural delete whenreview deleted.
Fixed tag bug wheresubject tag was getting deleted when delete all was being used.
Added GvReviewAsync, list and viewholder for dynamically loading views on the user feed screen as and when needed when scrolling.
Fixed caching bug introduced because of changing to retrieving partial reviewIds instead of full reviews for getReviews(). Caching partial reviews makes no sense.
Added comparator for GvReviewAsync
